con:config.con:query: SELECT ADDRID FROM (SELECT ADDR_ID AS ADDRID FROM MS_REP_ADDR ORDER BY ENTRY_DT DESC) WHERE ROWNUM = 1
SELECT FIRM_ID FROM (SELECT ROWNUM RN, FIRM_ID FROM MS_FIRM) WHERE RN=10
SELECT OFF_ID FROM (SELECT ROWNUM RN, OFF_ID FROM MS_OFFICE) WHERE RN=20
SELECT REP_ID FROM (SELECT ROWNUM RN, REP_ID FROM MS_REP) WHERE RN=10
SELECT EFF_DT FROM MS_TERRITORY_EFF_DT WHERE VALID_CONFIG_FLG='Y' AND CURRENT_CONFIG_FLG='Y'
SELECT * FROM MS_CHAN WHERE EFF_DT=(SELECT EFF_DT FROM MS_TERRITORY_EFF_DT WHERE VALID_CONFIG_FLG='Y' AND CURRENT_CONFIG_FLG='Y')

SELECT * FROM (SELECT OT.OFF_ID FROM MS_CHAN CH, MS_OFF_TERR OT WHERE CH.DIST_CHAN_CD=OT.DIST_CHAN_CD AND CH.EFF_DT = (SELECT EFF_DT FROM MS_TERRITORY_EFF_DT WHERE VALID_CONFIG_FLG='Y' AND CURRENT_CONFIG_FLG='Y') ORDER BY OT.UPD_DT DESC) WHERE ROWNUM=1

SELECT * FROM (SELECT RT.REP_ID FROM MS_CHAN CH, MS_REP_TERR RT WHERE CH.DIST_CHAN_CD=RT.DIST_CHAN_CD AND CH.EFF_DT =(SELECT EFF_DT FROM MS_TERRITORY_EFF_DT WHERE VALID_CONFIG_FLG='Y' AND CURRENT_CONFIG_FLG='Y') ORDER BY RT.UPD_DT DESC) WHERE ROWNUM=1
